c counting-v0 pigeonhole-3-2
c Variables x_{p,h} mean pigeon p is assigned to hole h.
c Variable number is 2*p + h + 1 for p in 0..2 and h in 0..1.
c Clauses require each pigeon to choose exactly one hole and no two pigeons
c to share a hole. This is the fixed 3-into-2 pigeonhole obstruction.
